Package Controller

Class AddAppointmentWindowController

  • java.lang.Object
    • Controller.AddAppointmentWindowController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class AddAppointmentWindowController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Joshua Breen C195 Project AddAppointmentWindowController this window is used to add appointments to the database and the program. Sets allContacts and allCustomers lists to be used for the combo boxes. MessageDisplay lambda is used to combine all error messages to the label used up here to make it easier if there are future changes, instead of changing it at each use. Start time is used for the combo boxes so they can start at 0:00.
